<div class="centered">
  <% if !flash[:notice].blank? %>
    <div class="alert alert-info">
      <%= flash[:notice] %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <h1 class="main-header">Welcome to the INCS Online Resume Bank. You may register for the 2018 INCS Teacher & Administrator Job Fair and/or register for the Resume Bank below</h1>

  <% if session[:user_id] != nil && User.find(session[:user_id]).access == 'pending' %>
    <p>Thank you for your registration. Please allow up to 2 business days for INCS staff to process approval of your account. You have received an email with further information.</p>
  <% end %>

  <% if session[:user_id] == nil %>
    <div class="main-container">
      <%= button_to "Candidate Resume Bank Registration", users_new_teacher_path, method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn"%>
      <%= button_to "Hiring Manager Registration", users_new_school_path, method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn"%>
    </div>
    <br>
  <% end %>

  <% if session[:user_id] != nil && User.find(session[:user_id]).access == 'teacher' && User.find(session[:user_id]).register2018 == 'bank' %>
    <div class="main-container">
    <%= button_to "Register for Job Fair", users_register_path, method: :post, class: "btn btn-info main-btn" %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <p class="main-content">
    <p class="main-content">
    The Illinois Network of Charter Schools (INCS) will host its 13th annual Teacher & Administrator Job Fair on <span class="boldBig">Saturday, April 7, 2018</span>. Representatives from charter schools across the state will be on hand to recruit hundreds of teachers, social workers, counselors, nurses, and other administrators. INCS seeks highly qualified candidates who are excited to work in a mission-drive environment and are ready to TEACH, LEAD, and SUCCEED. To upload your resume into our year-round database, please select “Candidate Resume Bank Registration” above.
    </p>
    <br>

    <p class="main-content">
      <strong>Teachers and Administrators will have the opportunity to:</strong>
      <ul class="main-content-list">
        <li>Meet recruiters from over 50 public charter schools representing over 120 campuses.</li>
        <li>Post your resume in the INCS Online Resume Bank, which is circulated to Illinois charter school hiring
managers year-round. To upload your resume into our year-round database, please select “Candidate
Resume Bank Registration” above.</li>
        <li>Interview on-site with schools looking to hire exceptional talent.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <p class="main-content">
      <strong>Schools will have the opportunity to:</strong>
      <ul class="main-content-list">
        <li>Meet with hundreds of educators.</li>
        <li>View candidates’ resumes ahead of time using the INCS Online Resume Bank (simply register by selecting “Hiring Manager Registration” above.</li>
        <li>Invite candidates for on-site interviews following the meet-and- greet portion of the event.</li>
        <li>School leaders may learn more about the fair and register <a href="https://www.incschools.org/events/tjf/">here</a></li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <p class="main-content"><strong>Agenda:</strong></p>
    <ul class="main-content-list">
      <li>8:30 am -9:30 am: School table set-up</li>
      <li>9:15 am - 10:00 am: Candidate registration</li>
      <li>10:00 am - 12:00 pm: Meet and Greet with candidates and schools</li>
      <li>12:00 pm - 1:30 pm: On-site teacher interviews (by invitation from charter school leaders only)</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="main-content"><strong>Location:</strong></p>
    <p class="main-content">
      <a href="http://pcsedu.org/MSA/about/location">Perspectives/IIT Math & Science Academy: 3663 South Wabash Avenue, Chicago, IL, 60653</a>
    </p>

    <p class="main-content"><strong>Parking:</strong></p>
    <p class="main-content">
      Parking is limited and public transportation is encouraged. Please be aware of permitted parking zones. Candidates are permitted to park in the school parking lot.
    </p>
    <br>

    <p class="main-content">
      Did you know INCS also has a <span class="bold">jobs board</span>? To browse current openings in Illinois charter public schools, please visit us <a href="https://www.incschools.org/jobs/jobs-at-charter-schools/">here</a>. To browse current openings at INCS, please visit us <a href="https://www.incschools.org/jobs/jobs-at-incs/">here</a>.
    </p>

    <p class="main-content">
      To find a charter public school near you, please visit us <a href="https://www.incschools.org/about-charters/find-a-charter-school/">here</a>.
    </p>

    <p class="main-content">
      If you have any questions about this tool or the Illinois Network of Charter Schools,  or would like to receive a 2017 Teacher Job Fair flyer, please contact Stephanie Arias, INCS Charter Support Manager, at <%=mail_to("SArias@incschools.org")%>
    </p>
  </p>

  <p class="main-content grayed">
    ABOUT INCS: The Illinois Network of Charter Schools (INCS) advocates for the improvement of public education by leveraging the charter school model as a catalyst to transform lives and communities. INCS works to ensure that charter public schools have adequate and equitable resources, the autonomy to find innovative approaches to meet student needs, and a fair and transparent policy landscape that allows high-quality options to thrive. As the voice of Illinois charter schools, INCS engages a diverse coalition of policymakers, school leaders, parents, and community members to create systemic change and secure high-quality schools for undeserved communities. Learn more about us <a target="_blank" href="https://www.incschools.org/">here</a>. 
  </p>


</div>
